Issues.Body:
### Which @angular/* package(s) are the source of the bug?

Don't known / other

### Is this a regression?

Yes

### Description

I created an Angular 17 SSR standalone project.  I needed to determine that the window.scrollY part was greater than 0. I had to use document with localStorage in dark and light mode, but I couldn't run it. When using @angular/universal, we could import anything we wanted, such as document, window and localStorage, with domino. I tried to transfer using different methods in the new SSR package, but I could not use the document and window sections in the application.


``` scrolled: boolean = false;
  constructor(
    private route: ActivatedRoute,
    @Inject(DOCUMENT) private document: Document,
  ) {
        if (typeof window !== 'undefined') {
          document.addEventListener('scroll', () => {
            this.scrolled = window.scrollY > 0;
          });
          var themeToggleDarkIcon = document.getElementById(
            'theme-toggle-dark-icon'
          );
          var themeToggleLightIcon = document.getElementById(
            'theme-toggle-light-icon'
          );
          if (
            localStorage.getItem('color-theme') === 'dark' ||
            (!('color-theme' in localStorage) &&
              window.matchMedia('(prefers-color-scheme: dark)').matches)
          ) {
            if (themeToggleLightIcon)
              themeToggleLightIcon.classList.remove('hidden');
          } else {
            if (themeToggleDarkIcon)
              themeToggleDarkIcon.classList.remove('hidden');
          }
      }
    
  }


  toggleMode() {
      if (typeof window !== 'undefined') {
        var themeToggleDarkIcon = document.getElementById(
          'theme-toggle-dark-icon'
        );
        var themeToggleLightIcon = document.getElementById(
          'theme-toggle-light-icon'
        );
        let mode = localStorage.getItem('color-theme');
        if (mode == 'light') {
          if (themeToggleDarkIcon)
            themeToggleDarkIcon.classList.remove('hidden');
          if (themeToggleLightIcon)
            themeToggleLightIcon.classList.add('hidden');
          localStorage.setItem('color-theme', 'dark');
          document.documentElement.classList.add('dark');
        } else if (mode == 'dark') {
          if (themeToggleDarkIcon) themeToggleDarkIcon.classList.add('hidden');
          if (themeToggleLightIcon)
            themeToggleLightIcon.classList.remove('hidden');
          localStorage.setItem('color-theme', 'light');
          document.documentElement.classList.remove('dark');
        } else {
          if (themeToggleDarkIcon) themeToggleDarkIcon.classList.add('hidden');
          if (themeToggleLightIcon)
            themeToggleLightIcon.classList.remove('hidden');
          localStorage.setItem('color-theme', 'light');
        }
      }
    
  }
```



